<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.6">
<l>yavarum yāvaiyu mellāp poruḷuṅ</l>
<l>kavarviṉṟi taṉṉu ḷoṭuṅka niṉṟa</l>
<l>pavarkoṇ ñāṉaveḷ ḷaccuṭar mūrtti</l>
<l>yavarem māḻiyam paḷḷi yārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He,</l> 
<l>the glowing form, a flood of pervasive knowledge</l>
<l>who stood retaining in himself without attachment</l>
<l>everyone, everything and all objects,</l>
	<l>is our ocean-bedded one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
